<hr>

My new book, <i>Algorithms Unlocked</i>, is out!  The Amazon site for
the book is <a
href="http://www.amazon.com/Algorithms-Unlocked-Thomas-H-Cormen/dp/0262518805/">here</a>,
and the MIT Press site is <a
href="https://mitpress.mit.edu/books/algorithms-unlocked">here</a>.

<p>

I maintain an <a href="au-bugs">errata page</a> for <i>Algorithms
Unlocked</i>.  If you find an error in the book and it's not already
in the <a href="au-bugs">errata page</a>, send email to <a
href="mailto:algorithms-unlocked@mit.edu">algorithms-unlocked@mit.edu</a>.
(The email address in the preface of the book is incorrect&mdash;the
first known error in the book.)

<p>

<i>Algorithms Unlocked</i> is the <a href="AU-10K.html">10,000th book
title published by MIT Press</a>.

<hr>

In the Spring 2013 term, I am teaching <a
href="http://www.cs.dartmouth.edu/~cs57">CS 57</a>: Compilers.

